Lead end to end testing activities and Customer Management 
Coordination with Business, IT, Vendors and Production Support team for review Requirements and Testing 
Estimation, Planning and scheduling Test phases of the work 
Strategize test approach and determining the testing methodology to test the requirements 
Own the testing process from Requirement phase through Storm support. 
Defect Management, Tracking & Generating Metrics using Defect Tracking tools like HP ALM, Jira etc. 
Perform risk analysis, Mitigation, issue management and escalation, when necessary 
Conduct reviews of Testing deliverables and Mentoring team about domain & test methods 
Project Monitoring, Query Tracking Issue tracking, Reporting Status and reviewing the delivered work 
Assess business requirements and perform feasibility study for Test Automation, Non-functional tests et al 
